author: The Current
description:
Justin Courtney Pierre of Motion City Soundtrack talks to Local Show Host Diane about his love for the idea stage in the creative process.

Check out Diane's full interview with the band talking about 'The Same Old Wasted Wonderful World,' their first album in 10 years, here:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9qcOwFRo1XM
title: Justin Courtney Pierre of Motion City Soundtrack talks about his love for the idea stage 💡#interview

author: The Current
description:
To celebrate The Current’s 20th Anniversary, The Current’s Live Sessions Vault unlocks never-before-seen live performance videos of bands and artists who have played in our iconic studio. 

Watch to see the full session, and interview, of Lizzo featuring previously unreleased footage, from when she visited The Current studio back in 2014.

Songs Performed 
00:00:00 Batches & Cookies
00:03:23 Interview Pt 1
00:14:57 Paris
00:18:09 Interview Pt 2
00:31:22 Faded
00:34:15 Interview Pt 3
